<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="conservation-n">conservation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌkɒnsə'veɪʃn/    美 /ˌkɑːnsər'veɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(自然资源的) 保护；管理；节约：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is a need for the <strong>conservation of</strong> trees, or there will soon be no forests.
保护树木大有必要，否则不用多久所有的森林就会消失。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Conservation of</strong> water is of great importance.
节约用水至关重要。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(艺术品、历史遗迹等的) 保存；保全：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the conservation of old buildings
古建筑的保护</p></div></div>